cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY 

This paper is primarily focused on robotics applications, specifically on online system identification from video. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also heavily relies on computer vision techniques, such as variational autoencoders, and machine learning techniques, such as recurrent neural networks, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with control policies and probabilistic predictions, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.SY (Systems and Control).
